# Regenerable build artifacts from tools/mesen-labels.py --asm (project the toml
# onto the native disasm). Deterministic from mesen-labels.toml + source/1-asm-6502/bank_NN.asm,
# so we don't version them. Regenerate: py -3 -m mesen-labels --asm (from tools/)
source/1-asm-6502/*_named.asm

# Rendered tactical fief maps (tools/batch-render-fief-maps.py) ARE versioned: small,
# and likely reused in the wiki. Regenerate after a renderer change:
#   py batch-render-fief-maps.py --scenario all

# Exception: raw in-game PPU captures kept only to validate the renderer's colors.
# Not versioned — they live here for local cross-checking, nothing more.
assets/maps/fiefs/ppu-render/
